                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-207-off1107 t18190915-207-crimeloc1110"></join>. On the 7th of September, the prisoner came to buy a book - he came three or four times. Next day he came, and saw me at the end of the shop; I missed a book, and asked him if he had taken it? He said No, and ran out of the shop.</p>
